<Content>Awful Service!!! The hotel changed the nightly rate without informing us until the very last night of our stay. I had no recourse because they already had my credit card. The hotel staff was discourteous and unprofessional. I had a lovely time in Mexico City otherwise. I do not recommend this hotel to anyone, there are plenty of other options available. 
